Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw studied Dinobot to the War Room, her eyes remaining their cold 
glare as they always were. A slight sneer appeared on her upper lip, just 
annoyed at her situation. She didn't like being near so many bots. She 
wasn't a bot that enjoyed the company of others. She turned into a harsh 
loner. That was the only option she had. That, or death.

She didn't like following the instant a bot snapped his fingers, but perhaps 
it was the only thing she could do right now. She had to follow Megatron's 
every word or be shot. She had taken her risks and took them hard. She 
activated her flight mode and came to his side, hovering when he stopped. 
The upper half of her fighting staff stuck out from her back as it always 
did.

"If you don't know anything, then take me to a bot that does," she said to 
him. "But tell me what you can."
